{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_07_beg","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":14,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_06_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-7","storyName":"群峦崩塌","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"铃兰将新的线索分享给众人。在众人思考之际，愤怒的民众擅自包围了十二音街道。同样受到民众威胁的泥岩小队开始向城镇出动，事态进一步恶化。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_07_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_07","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":12,"next":14,"characters":["亚叶","塞弗林","铃兰","塔佳娜","泥岩","萨卡兹战士","镇民","卡达","灰喉","叛乱的感染者","叛乱的镇民"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 7上","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Dialog","id":2},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"Character","name":"char_345_folnic_1#3","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"塞弗林，我需要知道天灾信使毕德曼的所有资料。","id":10,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":11},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"毕德曼......？为什么提起他？","id":12,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"1","id":13},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"有一位老爷爷说，他在暴乱中看到了负责指挥的毕德曼，是他们毁了动力炉。","id":14,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"2","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......老爷爷？可信度有多高？","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"他说，他是最后一个“冬灵人”......","id":18,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066#3","focus":"2","id":19},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":".......他，他还活着？不，很可能是冒牌货。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_066#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066#3","focus":"1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"那样的人是不会撒谎的......尽管这只是我的直觉，但我认为，他是不会撒谎的。","id":22,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"这是他的日记，和他的刀。我想会是个信物，所以擅自......","id":23,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"2","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"但他明明......","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"这真是出乎预料......我以为他和那些家伙都.......投湖自尽了。","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"我会去见他，我......我不知道，我该不该去见他？","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"老爷爷和我说了很多，他说，冬灵人并不是真正的罪魁祸首。","id":29,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"老爷爷也没有在恨你。说那些事的时候，他很平静。","id":30,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"2","id":31},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"我不是不能理解......但是那些叛乱分子的确在用“冬灵”作为他们掠夺的借口。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"那只是借口——","id":34,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"就算只是借口，他们也确实实施了暴行。下一步，他们将会要求我们开放粮仓，把一切席卷而空。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"何况冬灵的血脉早已与本地的沃伦姆德居民融合，事到如今......咳咳......","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"无论借口是什么，我们都只是不信任对方把握自己的命脉而已。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"一个本该死去的天灾信使，不仅活着，瞒着所有人，煽动了叛乱。","id":40,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"联系这一切来想，他是幕后黑手的可能性最大。","id":41,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......对，这下就说得通了，如果毕德曼真的还活着，他的确是那个可以煽动叛乱的人，他也知道沃伦姆德处于饥荒边缘的事实。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"动机呢？","id":45,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......大裂谷。","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"天灾发生之后，很多人都将城镇的损失怪罪于他。","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"在那短短数个月间，我们至少制止了七次针对他的暴力事件......而更多的，我们甚至不知详情。","id":49,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"在那之后，他几乎日日闭门不出，开始酗酒且有暴力倾向，直到......安托医生砸开了他家的门。","id":50,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"砸、砸开？","id":52,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"安托医生对处于低谷的毕德曼伸出了援手，那之后，毕德曼也时常去帮助安托医生的工作。","id":54,"figure":"avg_npc_066#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066#2","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"可听上去......他们的关系还不错？","id":56,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"至少表面如此，这也是我不曾怀疑过他的理由......毕德曼本来就是个很阴郁的家伙，就算陪着安托医生干活，我们也没见他笑过。","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"虽然理智的镇民和我本人都对他的工作表示理解，但......这也足以成为他报复我们的借口了。","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"情感上，他的报复动机毫无疑问是符合逻辑的，当然，这不说明任何事情。","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"几乎每一个人，都有想法和理由去报复另一个人。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......报复，又是报复。","id":63,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"而且......你也别说得这么事不关己。你确实说过，毕德曼死了。","id":64,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"你忽视了确认死者身份的工作，你忽视了这份可能性。","id":65,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"但现在还不能就这么认定——咳咳——咳咳——","id":67,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_066","focus":"1","id":68},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"您没事——","id":69,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":70},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":71},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"——慢着，等等。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"为什么外面的那些呐喊声停下了？","id":73,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"2","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":74},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":75},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"长官！","id":76,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"镇民们擅自行动，他们、他们打算包围十二音街道！","id":77,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"avg_npc_069#4","focus":"1","id":78},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"胡闹！去制止他们！","id":79,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"我们不知道现在躲藏在十二音街道是哪些人，万一那些“整合运动”已经蛰伏进了那里怎么办？","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"avg_npc_069#4","focus":"2","id":81},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"但，但他们都很激动，根本听不进话——！","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"他们不知从哪儿得知了“整合运动”的事情......！","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_069#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_066","name2":"avg_npc_069#4","focus":"1","id":84},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"嘁......一群光知道煽动的蠢货！","id":85,"figure":"avg_npc_066"},{"type":"stopmusic","time":"1","id":86},{"type":"Dialog","id":87},{"type":"Character","id":88},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltstrongpoint","screenadapt":"coverall","id":90},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":92,"musicid":1},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":93},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"城镇里的动静很大。","id":94,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"不仅如此......好像还有什么人找到这里来了。","id":95,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"既然都有组织民兵出城搜捕的决心......说明他们已经有了开战的打算。","id":96,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":97},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......那些镇民找到了这里，他们打算烧死我们。","id":98,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......烧死？","id":100,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":101},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"他们连车夫都懂得简单的法术，源石技艺是他们的义务教育内容，放把火，不难的事。","id":102,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......这里要待不下去了，会是罗德岛的人带头吗？","id":103,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":104},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......不会。","id":105,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"我倒觉得......只是这些愤怒的人，把我们当做罪魁祸首，把我们当做罪大恶极的感染者，来驱赶我们。","id":106,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"如此而已吧。","id":107,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"......泥岩。","id":109,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"别忘了，我们的同伴丧生在这座城镇中。","id":110,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们尊重你的选择，但你还年轻......你还不懂这其中的含义。","id":111,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"只是你要知道，我们的脾气也不是那么好的。","id":112,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":113},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......一旦动手，我们就会遭到整座城邦的追捕。","id":114,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"我们逃跑的话，就会被当作放火杀人，挑拨叛乱，抢劫城镇的元凶。一样的啊。","id":116,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......","id":118,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"按照正常的萨卡兹做派，很简单，我们只要毁了这座城镇就行，全部摧毁，这不难。","id":120,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"最麻烦的那些城防设备，自律施术单元，已经因为他们自己的内乱而停摆。","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"只要你下令，月亮将永远停留在冬灵山脉的荒野上，春天......不会来临。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......今年的冬天，会很长。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"现在，下决定，泥岩。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Dialog","id":127},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":128},{"type":"Character","id":129},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltalley","screenadapt":"coverall","id":130},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":132},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"false","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"抢回我们的家园！把感染者和土匪赶出去！","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"分发武器！男人们都来领，对自己源石技艺有自信的家伙都过来！","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_328_cammou","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"怎么回事？怎么感觉像是要去打仗一样？","id":137,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","id":138},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"差不多，就是打仗。","id":139,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":140},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"呜啊！灰喉姐，你能不能不要每次都这么悄无声息的？","id":141,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":142},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"至少他们自己觉得......他们在进行一场战争。","id":143,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"发生什么了？其他几位干员情况怎么样？","id":145,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":146},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"......不算太好，这场攻势似乎并不是塞弗林的决定，事情已经开始失去控制了......","id":147,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"亚叶说她找到了一些线索，这张照片，这个男人叫做毕德曼，现在是重要嫌疑人之一。","id":148,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"断崖已经开始单独行动了，记住，只要锁定这个人的位置，他很可能是叛乱的发起者。","id":149,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":150},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"找人是吧！明白！","id":151,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":152},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"——整合运动那边呢？","id":153,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"2","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"他们占着一座废弃的小猎村，每天都有人进进出出的，不过那个大块头倒是按兵不动。","id":155,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"卡达","text":"啊......但是我在找路的时候，似乎看见了一小撮人在城镇外巡逻......","id":156,"figure":"char_328_cammou"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_367_swllow_1","name2":"char_328_cammou","focus":"1","id":157},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"灰喉","text":"该不会......","id":158,"figure":"char_367_swllow_1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":159},{"type":"Dialog","id":160},{"type":"Character","id":161},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltstrongpoint","screenadapt":"coverall","id":163},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":164},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$frontline_intro","key":"$frontline_loop","volume":"0.4","id":165,"musicid":2},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","volume":"0.4","id":166},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":167},{"type":"playsound","key":"$smallearthquake","volume":"0.6","id":168},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":169},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":170},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"那、那是什么——！？","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"是石头？石头做的巨人？快，快用源石技艺——别用火啊！火肯定没用啊！","id":173,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"有没有懂得其他源石技艺的人在场！？快，拦住它！拦住那个怪物！","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Dialog","id":175},{"type":"Character","id":176},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":177},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","volume":"0.4","id":178},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":179},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":180},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":181},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","id":182},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":183},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":184},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":185},{"type":"Dialog","id":186},{"type":"Character","id":187},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"没有用，完全没有用！","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":190},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"所以说你们这些差生真的是——它们没有生命，只是源石技艺凝成的巨大岩石而已！","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"先去找出操纵者，然后把“留声机”抢回来！用那个对付它！","id":192,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Character","id":193},{"type":"Dialog","id":194},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":195},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":196},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":197},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":199},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_067","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"叛乱的感染者","text":"会让你们得逞吗！？","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_067"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"叛乱的感染者","text":"放弃吧！睁大眼睛看看，是什么让我们走到了今天的地步，是什么让沃伦姆德变成了废城！","id":202,"figure":"avg_npc_067"},{"type":"Dialog","id":203},{"type":"Character","id":204},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":205},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":206},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":207},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":208},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":209},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":210},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":211},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":212},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":213},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":214},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":215},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":216},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":217},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":218},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"不正是你们吗！？该死的冬灵人！串通感染者来篡夺城镇！","id":219,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_067","id":220},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"叛乱的感染者","text":"你们这群蠢货！满脑子音乐和艺术的废物！你们还没意识到沃伦姆德马上就要完蛋了吗！？","id":221,"figure":"avg_npc_067"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_068","id":222},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"我知道，但如果把城镇交给你们，完蛋得更快。","id":223,"figure":"avg_npc_068"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_067","id":224},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"叛乱的感染者","text":"塞弗林可曾向你们公布过粮食储备的情况！？可曾告诉你们我们何日能回到正轨？没有！我们没有希望了！","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_067"},{"type":"Dialog","id":226},{"type":"Character","id":227},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":228},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","volume":"0.4","id":229},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":230},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":231},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"1","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":232},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":234},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":235},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":236},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"就是你们这些人，毁了我的家——！","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_067","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"叛乱的镇民","text":"不！是你们这些高高在上的贵族老爷把我们逼得走投无路！","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_067"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_065","id":241},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"这就是你们随便行凶的理由吗！？","id":242,"figure":"avg_npc_065"},{"type":"Dialog","id":243},{"type":"Character","id":244},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$fightgeneral","text":"","id":245},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.2","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":247},{"type":"playsound","key":"$e_atk_magic_n","volume":"0.4","id":248},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"4","ystrength":"4","vibrato":"20","randomness":"30","fadeout":"true","id":249},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":250},{"type":"CameraShake","duration":"2","xstrength":"8","ystrength":"6","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":251},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":252},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_sp_ballista","id":253},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":254},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":255},{"type":"Dialog","id":256},{"type":"Character","id":257},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":258},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltroom","screenadapt":"coverall","id":259},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":260},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#2","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":261},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"——","id":262,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"亚叶姐姐！我们该去阻止他们！","id":263,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"既然有犯人的线索了，我们就不该这么互相伤害——","id":264,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"我们去说服他们，拦住那些靠近议事厅的人们，既然......既然他们知道罗德岛的事情，一定有办法——","id":265,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":266},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"——亚叶......姐姐？","id":267,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"为什么......要拉住我？","id":268,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"2","id":269},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......","id":270,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#3","focus":"1","id":271},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"如果再不制止的话——","id":272,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"2","id":273},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"亚叶","text":"......（默默摇头）","id":274,"figure":"char_345_folnic_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_358_lisa_1#3","name2":"char_345_folnic_1#4","focus":"1","id":275},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"铃兰","text":"......亚叶姐姐......？","id":276,"figure":"char_358_lisa_1#3"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":277},{"type":"Dialog","id":278},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":279},{"type":"Character","id":280},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_black","screenadapt":"coverall","id":281},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":282},{"type":"Text","text":"在战场上，生命的流逝速度很快，时间很短，不会有争论和谩骂的空间。","id":283},{"type":"Text","text":"不。","id":284},{"type":"Text","text":"是双方并不知道他们该争论什么。","id":285},{"type":"Text","text":"大家好像都不知道为什么要走上战场，为什么要白白送命......","id":286},{"type":"Text","text":"是啊......拿起武器之后，心怀理想的，其实是少数人而已。","id":287},{"type":"Text","text":"但现在，我的眼前，他们在交战，想杀死对方，也在大声地谩骂，诅咒，栽赃，推卸责任。","id":288},{"type":"Text","text":"真稀奇。","id":289},{"type":"Dialog","id":290},{"type":"Character","id":291},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_ltstreet1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":293},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":294},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":295,"musicid":3},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":296},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":297},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":298},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......走吧。","id":299,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":300},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"看你的态度......你还是不大情愿。","id":301,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"1","id":302},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"情愿......？我们从一开始不就只是想......不，从我们踏上沃伦姆德开始，说什么都没用。","id":303,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......我们在火灾里失去了四名感染者，我已经制止了很多，但现在，必须给其他感染者一个......态度。","id":304,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"否则我们很快会成为一盘散沙，不，怒火和欲望得不到安抚，甚至会变回那个......","id":305,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","name2":"avg_npc_053","focus":"2","id":306},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"萨卡兹战士","text":"你还真讨厌整合运动啊。那当时干嘛要入伙。","id":307,"figure":"avg_npc_053"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_011#2","id":308},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"......我以为......","id":309,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"算了。","id":310,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"泥岩","text":"该上战场了。","id":311,"figure":"avg_npc_011#2"},{"type":"Dialog","id":312},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":313},{"type":"Character","id":314},{"type":"Image","id":315}],"characters":["亚叶","塞弗林","铃兰","塔佳娜","泥岩","萨卡兹战士","镇民","卡达","灰喉","叛乱的感染者","叛乱的镇民"]}